{"tid":778225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【土耳其危機】拆局：土耳其購俄導彈防禦系統 美國小懲大戒","createTime":"2018-08-13T13:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T03:19:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e78e03cb897d5d08af173e650a5d291fcbef23","tid":778225,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:57:39.000Z","msg":"【土耳其危機】拆局：土耳其購俄導彈防禦系統 美國小懲大戒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2136125/%E3%80%90%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E3%80%91%E6%8B%86%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E8%B3%BC%E4%BF%84%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88%E9%98%B2%E7%A6%A6%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%20%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E6%87%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2136125%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%259C%259F%25E8%2580%25B3%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%25B1%2580%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%259C%259F%25E8%2580%25B3%25E5%2585%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E4%25BF%2584%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%25A6%25A6%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%2520%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2587%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%2592&d=3GyEJJVqm9wStTpq%2FW%2B7xDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=330ef22b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2136125/%E3%80%90%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E3%80%91%E6%8B%86%E5%B1%80%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E8%B3%BC%E4%BF%84%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88%E9%98%B2%E7%A6%A6%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%20%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E6%87%B2%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%92</a><br />\n<br />\n美國向土耳其實施新一輪制裁，令兩國關係惡化。美土兩國出現紛爭，除了美國牧師布朗森（Andrew Brunson）被土耳其囚禁這個表面原因外，背後更重要因素可能是土耳其堅決購買俄羅斯的導彈防禦系統。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其去年底與俄羅斯達成協議，以貸款模式向俄羅斯購買多套S-400導彈防禦系統，預料2020年初付運。<br />\n<br />\n這項協議觸動北約成員國的神經，因為北約使用的軍事設施系統與俄羅斯不同，俄羅斯很可能要派員到土耳其，協助土耳其運作系統，俄羅斯人員就有可能接觸到大量北約的軍事資料。<br />\n<br />\n再者，土耳其除了向俄羅斯購買導彈防禦系統，亦有向美國購買洛歇馬丁（Lockheed Martin）的F-35多用途隱形戰機，可能令F-35的機密資料亦落入俄羅斯手中，嚴重損害美國利益。<br />\n<br />\n盡管美國國會反對聲音強烈，美國至6月仍向土耳其出售F-35戰機，但土耳其已深知美國國會阻撓出售F-35戰機的力度只會愈來愈大，卻堅決購買俄羅斯的導彈防禦系統，更揚言會尋找F-35的替代品，儼如向美國挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n外界認為，土耳其購買俄羅斯的導彈防禦系統，不但讓俄羅斯有機竊取軍事資料，也會打擊美國的軍備銷量，因此才是美國制裁土耳其的主因。"},{"pid":"1ec9bbb2a3a47015de10fb76664d0a4a22815e2f","tid":778225,"uid":53466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:59:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a7e1c9690ec11e32e6e6132499b3b998fa95748","tid":778225,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ec9bbb2a3a47015de10fb76664d0a4a22815e2f","tid":778225,"uid":53466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:59:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"唔會俾到佢<br />\nf35b已經block左唔俾錢佢飛去土耳其<br />\nf35a好似只係派左機師去美國訓練，又係拎唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae682b84e322143cbe4af81fd92e3744e85c8936","tid":778225,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:03:46.000Z","msg":"想食兩家茶禮?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0b9294919308d04ad982865e8db761fd4e218b","tid":778225,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a7e1c9690ec11e32e6e6132499b3b998fa95748","tid":778225,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ec9bbb2a3a47015de10fb76664d0a4a22815e2f","tid":778225,"uid":53466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T13:59:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"唔會俾到佢<br />\nf35b已經block左唔俾錢佢飛去土耳其<br />\nf35a好似只係派左機師去美國訓練，又係拎唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"F35有零件係土耳其生產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310559f04f5d51eecdb75bbdc220a228ab3862c7","tid":778225,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma